OL,4,B`````````````````````````````````Rvhu
OL,5,CWOODLAND ACTION WEEK             Qjhhj 
OL,7, Did you know thatC5,000 years ago,Gthe 
OL,8, UK was covered in trees?               
OL,10, "It's hard to believe," sighsCJim Boot 
OL,11,Gfrom theCBritish Trust for Conservation
OL,12,CVolunteers,Gorganisers of Woodland     
OL,13, Action Week, 21 February to 1 March.   
OL,15, "Particularly when you consider that   
OL,16, today, onlyC7.5% of the country's      
OL,17,Cwoodlands remain.GIf we're not vigilant
OL,18, now, within a matter of years, that    
OL,19, too, will disappear."                  
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````1/6``
OL,21, C        by Bernadette Carroll         
OL,22,D]GMHANG OUT WITH THE GREEN SCENE p160  
