OL,1,Ru?bs`p5ppp*5j/%ppp`p0ppp`pp0ppV/o/o
OL,2,R7}jj75ws  j  7j!7j{57Rj 4j 
OL,3,R5jj}5|~  j|4}j 5j|45R5%e
OL,4,B`````````````````````````````````Rvhu
OL,5,CWOODLAND ACTION WEEK             Qjhhj 
OL,7, "If you want to find out who or what's 
OL,8, to blame for the frightening decay of  
OL,9, our woodlands,Cpoint the finger of     
OL,10,Cblame at mankind,"Gsays an angered Jim 
OL,11, Boot.                                  
OL,13, "People have had a huge impact -       
OL,14,Cclearing for agriculture, urban        
OL,15,CdevelopmentGand taking resources like  
OL,16, wood without replacing it.             
OL,18, "As a result,Cmuch has been lostGand   
OL,19, not just woods themselves."            
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````2/6``
OL,21,C  Green SceneG160      CEco SceneG148  
OL,22,D] GMWIN VEGGIE BACON & SAUSAGES p161   
