OL,5,CWOODLAND ACTION WEEK             Qjhhj 
OL,7,GThe British Trust for Conservation     
OL,8,GVolunteers has published aCWoodland    
OL,9,CAction packGwhich tells you their      
OL,10,Gvalue, threats and what you can do.    
OL,12,CTo obtain a pack,Gsend two first-class 
OL,13,Gstamps and your details to WAW Info    
OL,14,GPack, BTCV, 36 St Mary's St,           
OL,15,GWallingford, Oxon OX10 OEU.            
OL,17,BGIf you wish to join in more than 100 
OL,18,Gevents being held throughout the week, 
OL,19,Gcall the Trust onC01491 839766.        
